Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:03.500
The Nike Run Club app allows

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:04.500
 you to track the mileage of 

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:05.500
your shoes. 

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:07.500
Open your profile.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Go to My Shoes.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.000
The main screen shows each shoes'

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:14.000
mileage at a glance.

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:16.500
Selecting the shoe provides 

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:18.000
more details such as the number

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.000
of runs, average pace, and 

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.000
total time run on the shoes.


